description:
Game Intro: Revamped in 3D, the brand new Westward Journey Wokong version of Ocean King Online has been released with an all-round update. Keeping line with the cool and exciting gameplay of Ocean King game machine, it features cooler visual effects and more exciting fishing! “Left Chatting, Right Fishing” starts a new era of social fishing for all.
Fishing Info:
1: Random Super Weapon Mode: In fishing grounds, Mothership on the sea randomly drops three super weapons including Drill Cannon, Laser Cannon and Chain Depth Bomb at intervals. Successfully capture them to acquire corresponding skills of AOE damage;
Drill Cannon: Launches to move forward upon a random line for some time; deals penetrating damage to all types of fishes in the line with an extremely high rate to catch fishes;
Laser Cannon: Deals continuous laser damage to all fishes in a straight irradiation range; effectively catches big fishes and special fishes; performs best with Stasis skills;
Chain Depth Bomb: Deals AOE damage to all fishes for 2-6 times randomly; effectively catches middle and small fishes;
2: Maps of fishing grounds and types of fishes dynamically generates, which allows players to enjoy different journeys with an unknown sea area and fishes of hundred types!
3: Inheriting the consistent cool and exciting gameplay of Ocean King game machine, Ocean King Fishing Online mobile is an original rebuilding with 720p HD quality;
4: Ocean King Online offers various free supplies of Fish Coin including Daily Login, Online Rewards and the newly added gifts for Fishing King. Even if you only have 5 Fishing Coins, you can get rich quickly. Sudden Wealth or Comeback? It is up to Luck Fairy;
5: Line login and Facebook login is available in Ocean King Fishing Online, real social interactions!
our facebook page:https://www.facebook.com/OceanKingOnline/

