description:
You are in a boring day and decide to go to an adventure exploring the dungeon in front of your house!

*HOW TO PLAY*

-There are 3 buttons during the gameplay:
The 1° button you press to jump, the 2° you press to slide, and the button with the sword you attack;
-To get the golden apples coin you just need to run the farest you can;
-To get the zombie heads you just need to kill them.

*FEATURES*
-Global leaderboard ( the best runner, the one who killed the most and the one who has more skins unlocked);
-TONS of skins to buy ( we will keep adding new skins every update);
-Two types of money: golden apples and zombie heads;

