description:
To whom it may concern! Next generation of a cult classic game is out! 

The smallest match3 ever! Only 7 mb of endless fun!

This "match 3" is unlike any other. Moving field, color changing elements, chill music. Ready for binge playing in multiple modes. Add excitement to you life! 

The game features: 
- the most unlimited gameplay ever, immerse into speed and drive like there is no tomorrow;
- 20 difficulty levels to choose from, from any level of expertise are welcome to hard-core advanced; 
- prey your competitiveness on your friends - play together and have fun; 
- three meditation modes - focus on gaming quality not quantity. 

Our game comes with only one in-app purchase, which instantly provides access to all cosmic entertainment! 

Beware! Huge amounts of time may and will be wasted.

Heli Runner it's a cross platform game which was developed in classic (like “Line Runner”) casual genre. Use only two fingers to control helicopter and chain for picking up the cars. Try to catch bonuses and avoid clouds in the sky. Earn extra lives absorbing the cars. The flight is happening in front of the countryside background decorated by realistic physics. Finally, now it's the best time to try it!

Game features:

- 5 levels with different clouds density;
- 9 car types;
- system for earning extra lives and bonuses;
- realistic physics;
- possibility to save users records.

How to play:

- use two screen buttons to control helicopter and chain.

